text: Seo Yea-ji (서예지, born April 6, 1990) is a South Korean actress. She is known for her roles in the television series Diary of a Night Watchman (2014), Save Me (2017), Lawless Lawyer (2018), and It's Okay to Not Be Okay (2020). She also known for her roles in movies The Throne (2015), Another Way (2017), and By Quantum Physics: A Nightlife Venture (2019). ==References== ==Other websites== * Seo Yea-ji at Gold Medalist Category:1990 births Category:South Korean television actors Category:South Korean movie actors Category:Actors from Seoul Category:Living people
